223000740110@unknown@formal@none@1@S@For instance, character n-gram hash codes may be computed at a cost of only a couple assignments and arithmetic operations per character by the <a>Karp-Rabin algorithm</a>, which only implicitly represent the n-grams themselves.@@@@1@33@@danf@4-5-2012
